OL,3,CMan who murdered university lecturer
OL,4,Closes appeal bid over 'harsh' sentence
OL,6,FA doorman who was jailed for life for
OL,7,Fmurdering his estranged wife after
OL,8,Fmonths of stalking and harassing her
OL,9,Fhas lost a bid to have his sentence
OL,10,Freduced.
OL,12,FPaul Antony Butler was imprisoned for
OL,13,Fat least 27 years in April last year
OL,14,Fafter admitting to stabbing university
OL,15,Flecturer Claire Chick more than 20
OL,16,Ftimes with a kitchen knife outside her
OL,17,Fhome in Plymouth in January 2025.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
