FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778609470
OL,3,CMan who murdered university lecturer
OL,4,Closes appeal bid over 'harsh' sentence
OL,6,FProsecutors told Butler's sentencing
OL,7,Fhearing at the city's crown court that
OL,8,Fbefore her murder, Claire had endured
OL,9,Fmonths of harassment, stalking and
OL,10,Fviolence at the 54-year-old's hands
OL,11,Fand had made six statements to the
OL,12,Fpolice about his conduct.
OL,14,FSentencing him in April last year,
OL,15,FJudge Robert Linford said that
OL,16,FButler's actions were "nothing less
OL,17,Fthan sheer murderous brutality"
OL,18,Ffollowing a relationship of "obsession
OL,19,Fand control".
OL,26,@xD@WOUyD@_O]zD@]OU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778609470
OL,3,CMan who murdered university lecturer
OL,4,Closes appeal bid over 'harsh' sentence
OL,6,FButler sought to challenge the length
OL,7,Fof his sentence, telling the Court of
OL,8,FAppeal in written submissions that he
OL,9,Fbelieved it was "excessively harsh",
OL,10,Fbut three senior judges dismissed the
OL,11,Fappeal bid on Tuesday (May 12).
OL,13,FJudge Kristina Montgomery KC, sitting
OL,14,Fwith Lord Justice Singh and Mr Justice
OL,15,FPicken, said there were "numerous
OL,16,Faggravating features" in the case,
OL,17,Fconcluding: "There are no arguable
OL,18,Fgrounds for saying that the sentence
OL,19,Fwas manifestly excessive."
OL,26,@qD@QOUqD@cO]wD@YOUxD@UO]yD@MOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778609470
OL,3,CMan who murdered university lecturer
OL,4,Closes appeal bid over 'harsh' sentence
OL,6,FButler did not attend the hearing in
OL,7,Fperson and was not represented.
OL,9,FPlymouth Crown Court heard that Butler
OL,10,Fand Claire, a lecturer in nursing at
OL,11,Fthe University of Plymouth, became
OL,12,Fneighbours in 2021, were a couple the
OL,13,Ffollowing year, and married in 2024.
OL,15,FBut the marriage soon broke down,
OL,16,Fprosecutors said, with Butler later
OL,17,Farrested three times for assault,
OL,18,Fharassment and stalking of Claire,
OL,19,Fincluding for placing a tracking
OL,20,Fdevice on her car.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778609470
OL,3,CMan who murdered university lecturer
OL,4,Closes appeal bid over 'harsh' sentence
OL,6,FWith his escalating behaviour, Claire
OL,7,Ftold police in her final statement the
OL,8,Fday before she was killed: "I only
OL,9,Ffeel that Butler will kill me if
OL,10,Ffurther action is not taken. I am in
OL,11,Ffear of leaving my house."
OL,13,FAfter learning Claire had formed a new
OL,14,Frelationship, Butler went to her flat
OL,15,Fwearing a camouflaged hooded top and
OL,16,Fwaited for her to come out of the
OL,17,Fbuilding.
OL,26,@pD@\OUsD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778609470
OL,3,CMan who murdered university lecturer
OL,4,Closes appeal bid over 'harsh' sentence
OL,6,FHe then attacked her in the street and
OL,7,Falso chased Claire's new partner, who
OL,8,Fwitnessed the murderous assault,
OL,9,Fshouting at him: "I'll f****** do you
OL,10,Ftoo."
OL,12,FButler was arrested the following day
OL,13,Fat a hotel in Liskeard and told
OL,14,Fpolice: "She trusted me and she loved
OL,15,Fme and I can't believe I have done
OL,16,Fthis.
OL,18,F"She has children and grandchildren `
OL,19,FI have destroyed so many lives. I
OL,20,Fdon't care about me."
OL,26,@qD@ROUrD@EO]vD@IOUzD@AOU|D@UO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
