FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778609470
OL,3,CMan who murdered university lecturer
OL,4,Closes appeal bid over 'harsh' sentence
OL,6,FHe added: "I am a monster. I have just
OL,7,Fseen hell, I am going to hell. This is
OL,8,Fwhat I am going to look forward to."
OL,10,FMore than a dozen officers were served
OL,11,Fwith misconduct or gross misconduct
OL,12,Fnotices in January this year over
OL,13,FDevon and Cornwall Police's contact
OL,14,Fwith Claire Chick.
OL,26,@nD@KOUpD@dO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
