PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778609470
OL,3,CMan who murdered university lecturer
OL,4,Closes appeal bid over 'harsh' sentence
OL,6,FThese included 15 police officers, two
OL,7,Fpolice staff members and one former
OL,8,Fofficer, who were involved in logging
OL,9,Finformation, risk assessments and
OL,10,Fsafeguarding decisions made about
OL,11,FClaire from September 2024 until just
OL,12,Fbefore her death.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
